<taxonomicNameLabel box="[510,591,1370,1394]" pageId="2" pageNumber="595" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
A. Male; B. Female. Scale bar: 2 mm.
</paragraph>
</caption>
