<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,275,2018,2042]" pageId="2" pageNumber="595">FIGURE 3.</emphasis>
Male genitalia of 
<taxonomicName authority="Yuan &amp; Zheng &amp; Ma &amp; Gu, 2022" authorityName="Yuan &amp; Zheng &amp; Ma &amp; Gu" authorityYear="2022" box="[461,571,2018,2042]" class="Insecta" family="Trigonidiidae" genus="Trigonidium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="595" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nigripes" status="sp. nov.">
